        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This **completely** misses the point of my question. The question **WAS NOT** \"why would anyone want to build neovim with Nix?\"\r\n\r\nThe question was why should 10% of the code needed to build neovim with Nix live in neovim/neovim while 90% of that code lives in Nixpkgs? Wouldn't it be simpler for the Neovim team AND the Nix team if 100% of this code lives in the Nix repos?",
            "created_at": "2023-12-23T00:08:38Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/26702#issuecomment-1868143257",
            "id": 1868143257,
            "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/issues/26702",
